rows.label: qst106017_msg0001
rows.name:
Dad, what you mean by
getting Hana ready?

rows.label: qst106017_msg0002
rows.name:
Exercises? Hana always ready
for warm-up exercises!

rows.label: qst106017_msg0004
rows.name:
Hana thought maybe need to do
exercises to get ready for big upgrade...

rows.label: qst106017_msg0006
rows.name:
Artificial Blade not need exercises!
As long as joints not rusty, always
ready to operate at full capacity!

rows.label: qst106017_msg0007
rows.name:
Anyway, Tora. Please take Hana
and go to Goldmund Flight Deck
in Avaritia.

rows.label: qst106017_msg0009
rows.name:
Hana need to enroll in Bluesky
Nopon University for a day.

rows.label: qst106017_msg0011
rows.name:
Listen close, Hana. To become true
lady, proper education is essential!

rows.label: qst106017_msg0012
rows.name:
Learn many thing at Bluesky Nopon
University, and become educated!

rows.label: qst106017_msg0013
rows.name:
Is possible to become educated
in only one day...?

rows.label: qst106017_msg0014
rows.name:
Tora... Is it not necessity for sake of
upgrade to send Hana to university,
even if only for one day?

rows.label: qst106017_msg0016
rows.name:
Well then, Hana. Go learn many thing
from teacher Fuwafuwa at Bluesky
Nopon University!

rows.label: qst106017_msg0017
rows.name:
Understood! Hana will become
perfect lady!
